 of doubts and Penelope as a woman of great depth and strength.  aMode of access: Internet via World Wide Web.  aIn English.0 aDescription based on online resource; title from PDF title page (publisher's Web site, viewed 21. Jun 2021) 7aLITERARY CRITICISM / General.2bisacsh  abattle of wills with wife.  abecomes furious for not trusting.  acaptivating.  aclassic mythology.  afirst person reflections.  ajealousy.  alack of faith.  alegendary homeric hero.  aman full of doubts.  amisgivings.  aodysseus returns to ithaca.  aodysseus.  apenelope rises as major force.  apenelope.  aplays game of fictions.  arecognizes guise of beggar.  aretelling of odyssey.  aridding palace of suitors.  aself doubt.  astruggle for respect and supremacy.  awoman of great depth and strength.08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2019 Englishz978311061076508iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2019z9783110664232oZDB-23-DGG08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Literary, Cultural and Area Stud. 2019 Englishz978311061036908iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertEBOOK PACKAGE Literary, Cultural and Area Studies 2019z9783110606348oZDB-23-DKU08iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertUCA Complete eBook-Package 2019z978311065207908iTitle is part of eBook package:dDe GruytertUniversity of California Press Complete eBook-Package 2019z978311066763940uhttps://doi.org/10.1525/9780520972810zCo-access DOI >> click Walter de Gruyter40uhttps://www.degruyter.com/isbn/9780520972810423Coveruhttps://www.degruyter.com/cover/covers/9780520972810.jpg  a978-3-11-061036-9  EBOOK PACKAGE Literary, Cultural and Area Stud. 2019 Englishb2019  a978-3-11-061076-5  EBOOK PACKAGE COMPLETE 2019 Englishb2019  a978-3-11-065207-9  UCA Complete eBook-Package 2019b2019  a978-3-11-066763-9  University of California Press Complete eBook-Pack